{"tid":1471222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你地唔撚好再討論鬼唔鬼，做得岩定錯。咁撚驚失民意，唔該幫手搶高地","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:06:27.000Z","uid":98507,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a99dd3599e998ec753c72f1084543409a987de3","tid":1471222,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"咁多次行動，次次都話失民意<br />\n係呀真係有可能失民意<br />\n但點解最後冇失？<br />\n係因為有鍵盤戰士出黎鋪天蓋地咁維護手足呀<br />\n你搶到道德高地，你做乜撚都岩<br />\n所以唔好再討論尋晚有冇做錯<br />\n有冇做錯就係睇邊個佔到高地，唔該快手打輿論戰，唔好輸比對家<br />\n黎緊仲有818，又話要搞多次百萬人大遊行？<br />\n屌你地望下自己而家做緊乜撚？星期三喇<br />\n你而家唔開始<br />\n818連50萬都冇呀"},{"pid":"2d97293af696c1a76c6ada40485dd3d20f9d139b","tid":1471222,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48559dbd49ded0d8deadf5bd61beda23f5623021","tid":1471222,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba